<note type="sourceStatus" xml:id="sourceStatus">
<p>Original manuscript</p></note>
<note type="location" xml:id="location">
<p>Amsterdam, Van Gogh Museum, inv. no. b8382 V/2006</p></note>
<note type="date" xml:id="date">
<p>Van Gogh wrote his terse note actually on Van Rappard’s letter of 24 May <ref target="let503.xml">(503)</ref>, which he had ‘just’ received. This means that in all likelihood his reply was written one day later than the letter, which is why we have dated it Monday, 25 May 1885. </p></note></vg:letDesc></sourceDesc></fileDesc></teiHeader>
